These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, mauve
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | snowmobile     | trike     |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | electronic |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani  |
| Pet           | horse    | chinchilla |
| Color         | mauve   | brown       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, purple
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
2 different pets are kept: dog, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person who likes orange##1
3. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| Color           | purple  | orange     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | action      |
| Pet           | dog        | lizard      |
| Flower         | poppy | zinnia     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, mexican
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse
City: boston, new-york
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the dressmaker is the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar         | ritmeester     | montecristo    |
| Job           | doctor     | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese   |
| Sport         | basketball | lacrosse   |
| City     | boston | new-york |

