The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
