The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage      | tea        | fanta     |
| City           | paris   | venice |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | horror    |
| Hobby           | hiking    | skydiving    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | surfing   |

