2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the american is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
