The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, doctor
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, tram
1. the doctor is the fan of country##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Game      | domino      | billiard     |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | country  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Job         | software-developer | doctor |
| Transport     | ship     | tram     |

 